CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg.1 reads:" President Kennedy Stumps Area for Democrats - Leaving By Air Force 707 Jet, President Kennedy stops to greet the crowd at Pittsburgh's main airport."
TitMainTitle: President John F. Kennedy exiting Air Force One at Pittsburgh airport for presidential campaign visit
